### Hero Slides API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3010

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3010
@token = Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

# =================================
# PUBLIC ENDPOINTS (No auth required)
# =================================

### Get Active Slides (Public)
# @name getActiveSlides
GET {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides/active
Content-Type: application/json

###

# =================================
# PROTECTED ENDPOINTS (Auth required)
# =================================

### Get All Slides (Admin)
# @name getAllSlides
GET {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Get Slide by ID
# @name getSlideById
GET {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides/SLIDE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Create New Slide
# @name createSlide
POST {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Nuevo Slide de Prueba",
  "subtitle": "Subtítulo del slide",
  "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589244159943-460088ed5c92?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop",
  "order": 3,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Update Slide
# @name updateSlide
PUT {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides/SLIDE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Título Actualizado",
  "subtitle": "Nuevo subtítulo",
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Update Multiple Slides (Bulk - for reordering)
# @name updateMultipleSlides
PUT {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "slides": [
    {
      "_id": "SLIDE_ID_1",
      "order": 0
    },
    {
      "_id": "SLIDE_ID_2",
      "order": 1
    },
    {
      "_id": "SLIDE_ID_3",
      "order": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Delete Slide
# @name deleteSlide
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides/SLIDE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Initialize Default Slides (if none exist)
# @name initializeDefaultSlides
POST {{baseUrl}}/hero-slides/initialize
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###
